basic.color: Flower color light red to cyan purple, mixed with light yellow, leaf color green or with purple red

maintenance.soil: Acidic soil with loose texture or soil with specific nutrients
maintenance.sunlight: Resistant to half shade, put in places with scattered light
maintenance.watering: Water thoroughly after soil surface dries, avoid saturated water
maintenance.fertilization: Dilute fertilizers following instructions, apply 1-2 times monthly
maintenance.pruning: Remove aged tissues, dead, rotten, diseased leaves timely
